3
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:38,920
[Episode 6]

4
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:47,350
It's me.

5
00:01:48,030 --> 00:01:48,800
Well,

6
00:01:49,190 --> 00:01:50,320
I have good news for you.

7
00:01:50,830 --> 00:01:52,190
I passed the assessment.

8
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,760
Pretty impressive, huh?

9
00:01:54,830 --> 00:01:55,800
I'm such a genius.

10
00:01:57,830 --> 00:01:58,440
Congratulations.

11
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,480
Are you done with work?

12
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,390
I'm at your door.

13
00:02:03,390 --> 00:02:04,120
(Did you come to me?)

14
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,000
No.

15
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:07,550
I was just passing by.

16
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:09,840
When are you free?

17
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:11,320
It's only right and proper

18
00:02:11,390 --> 00:02:12,710
for me to treat you to a meal

19
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:14,560
to thank you.

20
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:15,520
Not today.

21
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,880
I'm on a business trip out of town.

22
00:02:20,110 --> 00:02:21,670
If you don't want to come, just say so.

23
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,840
Don't make such an excuse.

24
00:02:24,350 --> 00:02:25,390
I'm really on a business trip.

25
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:28,030
We can eat together

26
00:02:28,070 --> 00:02:28,880
when I get back tomorrow night.

27
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:33,960
All right.

28
00:02:35,070 --> 00:02:35,750
See you tomorrow night.

29
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,200
(Dear passengers,)

30
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:48,950
(the train is about to arrive
at Baiyang County station.)

31
00:02:49,510 --> 00:02:50,680
(Passengers)

32
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,560
(for Baiyang County station,)

33
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:52,920
