34
00:02:53,230 --> 00:02:54,280
(and prepare to get off.)

35
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:33,400
[Baiyang County]

36
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:57,710
Mrs. Jiang.

37
00:04:00,470 --> 00:04:01,280
Long time no see.

38
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:02,430
Lian?

39
00:04:04,710 --> 00:04:05,000
It's me.

40
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:05,840
I haven't seen you

41
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,800
for a long time.

42
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,750
I can hardly recognize you.

43
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:11,590
Lian.

44
00:04:12,150 --> 00:04:12,680
Let me get you some water.

45
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:13,750
Mrs. Jiang, please sit down.

46
00:04:14,150 --> 00:04:14,910
No need.

47
00:04:15,310 --> 00:04:15,590
Please sit down.

48
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:17,080
Sit down.

49
00:04:18,150 --> 00:04:19,430
Well...

50
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,080
Lian.

51
00:04:28,750 --> 00:04:30,310
Do you know where Xiaoyuan is?

52
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:32,960
It's been a year,

53
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,840
and I haven't heard from her.

54
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,560
I can't reach her on the phone.

55
00:04:39,310 --> 00:04:40,190
Someone said

56
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,030
she's also in trouble.

57
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,240
Don't worry.

58
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:46,870
Just tell me.

59
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:47,870
Mrs. Jiang.

60
00:04:48,710 --> 00:04:49,800
Xiaoyuan is fine.

61
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,360
I saw her a few days ago.

62
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,520
That's good.

63
00:04:58,960 --> 00:04:59,470
Is she in

64
00:04:59,470 --> 00:05:01,280
some kind of trouble?

65
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,080
It's been so long.

66
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:07,630
Why hasn't she come back to see me?

67
00:05:43,470 --> 00:05:44,030
When was

68
00:05:44,030 --> 00:05:44,800
the last time

69
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:45,870
Xiaoyuan came to see you?

70
00:05:47,590 --> 00:05:48,590
Almost a year ago.

71
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:49,680
At that time,

72
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,030
I was seriously ill,

73
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:52,680
almost at death's door.

74
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,160
She came back

75
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:56,920
without telling anyone

76
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:59,390
and left me 100,000 yuan.

77
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,870
When Xiaoyuan got into college,

78
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,240
I was seriously ill,

79
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:07,310
undergoing surgery and hospitalization.

80
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:10,240
Money was running out like water.

81
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,680
She suffered a lot during that time.

82
00:06:14,270 --> 00:06:15,870
(She insisted on leaving home
to earn money)

83
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:17,630
(to pay for my treatment.)

84
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:18,480
(She was out there)

85
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,830
(without a college degree.)

86
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,680
(What kind of job could she get?)

87
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:22,870
(The jobs she found)

88
00:06:22,870 --> 00:06:24,070
(were all about physical work.)

89
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:25,870
(She was stubborn)

90
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,430
(and wouldn't listen to me.)

91
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,310
Why did you come so late?

92
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,070
It's on me today.

93
00:06:59,270 --> 00:07:00,040
What's the matter?

94
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,360
I got a month's pay.

95
00:07:03,310 --> 00:07:04,510
If I remember correctly,

96
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,480
you only make 2,000 yuan

97
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:07,390
a month.

98
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:09,630
2,000 yuan is enough

99
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,480
to treat you to dinner.

100
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,360
Besides, I've been promoted
to intern stylist.

101
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:13,720
Next month,

102
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,830
I'll receive the performance bonus.

103
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,040
I treat you to dinner

104
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:19,390
mainly to express

105
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:20,510
my sincere gratitude.

106
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:22,600
According to tradition,

107
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,070
let me drink three toasts to you.

108
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,560
Thank you for generously imparting
your knowledge to me.

109
00:07:27,870 --> 00:07:29,390
If you hadn't taught me well,

110
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:30,310
I wouldn't have

111
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,600
passed the assessment so smoothly.

112
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,870
I remember you didn't drink before.

113
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:40,000
I didn't, but I do now.

114
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:40,630
And sometimes,

115
00:07:40,630 --> 00:07:41,920
work requires it.

116
00:07:44,630 --> 00:07:45,920
(She's a girl.)

117
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,920
(What good job can she find)

118
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,240
(that pays 100,000 in one go?)

119
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,680
(The last time she came back,)

120
00:07:55,190 --> 00:07:56,240
she seemed different.

121
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,390
She picked up

122
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:02,070
smoking and drinking.

123
00:08:02,630 --> 00:08:03,630
People in the village even said

124
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:04,830
that she's gone astray.

125
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,630
Well,

126
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,630
this kid

127
00:08:11,630 --> 00:08:12,920
dropped out of school

128
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:13,920
just for

129
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,630
my lowly life.

130
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:17,720
(If I had known,)

131
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,720
(I would have died.)

132
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,000
The second toast.

133
00:08:34,950 --> 00:08:35,830
Drinking too much is bad for your health.

134
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,160
I appreciate it.

135
00:08:37,430 --> 00:08:37,950
You don't have to

136
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:38,800
be so formal with me.

137
00:08:40,800 --> 00:08:41,240
By the way,

138
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:43,720
here's the 713 yuan I owe you.

139
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:44,360
Take it.

140
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:57,360
I said I'd drink three toasts to you.

141
00:08:58,040 --> 00:08:59,000
I never

142
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,120
take advantage of others,

143
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,120
and I always

144
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,830
keep my promises.

145
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:14,720
Jiang Xiaoyuan.

146
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:16,270
Let's talk.

147
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:18,830
There's nothing to talk about.

148
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:20,950
Do you want to bring up the past again?

149
00:09:23,430 --> 00:09:25,040
I just want to treat you to dinner.

150
00:09:25,430 --> 00:09:26,800
Besides, everyone has secrets.

151
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,040
I won't pry into yours,

152
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:29,070
and you shouldn't pry into mine.

153
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:29,830
Can't we do that?

154
00:09:30,390 --> 00:09:31,720
I'm not obligated to tell you everything

155
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:33,270
about my life, am I?

156
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:34,560
That's right.

157
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:36,600
You're not obligated to do that.

158
00:09:39,190 --> 00:09:40,480
What about the past?

159
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:43,560
Don't you have any questions

160
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:44,310
to ask me?

161
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,560
(Was there any conflict)

162
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,800
(or emotional entanglement)

163
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:50,190
(between the previous Jiang Xiaoyuan
and him?)

164
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:51,920
No.

165
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:57,600
But I've been waiting for you to ask me

166
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:58,630
why I didn't show up

167
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:00,240
six years ago,

168
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:01,040
why I left

169
00:10:01,070 --> 00:10:02,160
without saying goodbye,

170
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:04,560
why I never came back
to Baiyang County,

171
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,270
and why I knew

172
00:10:07,310 --> 00:10:08,240
you needed help

173
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,270
but still were gone for four years.

174
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:13,000
Even when I came back,

175
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:13,840
I didn't

176
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,910
come to you immediately.

177
00:10:16,790 --> 00:10:18,030
(The thing is I don't know)

178
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,360
(what happened.)

179
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:25,840
Jiang Xiaoyuan,

180
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,000
you said you always keep your promises,

181
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,600
and I believe I do too.

182
00:10:31,750 --> 00:10:33,480
But I've gone back on my word.

183
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:35,600
Don't you want to

184
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,320
ask me why?

185
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,120
Let's not talk about it.

186
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:44,960
Let's eat.

187
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,600
Jiang Xiaoyuan.

188
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:55,360
If you blame me

189
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,240
for not keeping my promise,

190
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:56,910
you can hit me or scold me.

191
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,000
You can take it out on me as you want.

192
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,030
But can you stop

193
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:00,670
acting like

194
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:02,000
you don't know anything?

195
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:04,670
Are you finished?

196
00:11:05,270 --> 00:11:05,870
I've said

197
00:11:05,910 --> 00:11:07,440
that I don't want to bring up the past.

198
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:07,910
Besides,

199
00:11:07,910 --> 00:11:09,200
I told you earlier,

200
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:11,360
but you don't believe it.

201
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,390
Qi Lian.

202
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,840
I'm only treating you to dinner.

203
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,270
Why are you treating me like this?

204
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:32,550
I know you feel guilty

205
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:33,910
about the former Jiang Xiaoyuan.

206
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:34,870
You can't forget her,

207
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:36,150
and that's why

208
00:11:36,270 --> 00:11:37,080
you've been so good to me.

209
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,670
But I've told you

210
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:40,150
I'm not that Jiang Xiaoyuan.

211
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,440
I don't know

212
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,630
what happened to her,

213
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,630
and I can't respond to you

214
00:11:43,630 --> 00:11:45,120
on behalf of her.

215
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:47,360
If you feel like
you're at a disadvantage,

216
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:50,000
we can just end it.

217
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:54,960
Jiang Xiaoyuan.

218
00:11:56,870 --> 00:11:57,870
You still don't get it.

219
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,080
I've never felt

220
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,080
that I've been at a disadvantage.

221
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,480
It's such a big umbrella.

222
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,910
Can't we use it together?

223
00:12:27,710 --> 00:12:29,180
♪Hey♪

224
00:12:30,820 --> 00:12:32,560
♪When you're helpless♪

225
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,530
♪Hey♪

226
00:12:37,450 --> 00:12:39,000
♪I'm here♪

227
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:41,480
I won't ask anymore.

228
00:12:43,750 --> 00:12:44,440
I won't ask anymore.

229
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,910
I won't ask about the past.

230
00:12:48,230 --> 00:12:51,110
♪I'm getting closer♪

231
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:52,200
Jiang Xiaoyuan.

232
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,550
Although we can't go back to the past，

233
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,960
we can still be friends

234
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:00,840
in the future,

235
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:03,600
right?

236
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:07,960
Let go of me first.

237
00:13:22,150 --> 00:13:23,150
To be frank,

238
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,390
I have no family

239
00:13:25,390 --> 00:13:26,200
in this world,

240
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:28,030
and I really need friends.

241
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,790
And you're the first person

242
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:30,750
to reach out

243
00:13:30,750 --> 00:13:31,840
to me.

244
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:33,440
But I hope

245
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,440
you can see us

246
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:36,440
as new friends,

247
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:37,550
rather than you making concessions

248
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:39,390
to your old lover.

249
00:13:40,150 --> 00:13:41,910
I'm not her.

250
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:44,080
Can you understand?

251
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:54,790
♪I could just go anywhere with you♪

252
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:58,270
♪'Cause you're my favorite thing to do♪

253
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:01,540
♪Like moonlight in my hand♪

254
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:03,790
I understand.

255
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:06,960
I promise you.

256
00:14:10,270 --> 00:14:12,080
Friends will go through

257
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,510
thick and thin together.

258
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:16,960
Do you need to think it through?

259
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:21,240
If you need anything,
you can come to me.

260
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:22,720
I...

261
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,510
I mean it's mutual,

262
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:26,910
not me

263
00:14:26,910 --> 00:14:27,840
taking advantage of you.

264
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:32,870
You've always been fair,

265
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,080
and you keep your promises.

266
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:39,790
Okay.

267
00:14:41,270 --> 00:14:42,240
From now on,

268
00:14:42,270 --> 00:14:43,840
we're friends.

269
00:14:48,010 --> 00:14:49,730
♪Waiting for you♪

270
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:55,120
Friends.

